{"word":"G4756 - στρατιά - stratiá - strat-ee'-ah - Host","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">στρατιά</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">stratiá</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">strat-ee'-ah</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Host</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Noun Feminine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (பெண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"சேனை - பெண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"1. an army, band of soldiers"},{"paragraph":"2. the poets equivalent to strateia"},{"paragraph":"3. the host of heaven"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Feminine of a derivative of <b>&#x03C3;&#x03C4;&#x03C1;&#x03B1;&#x03C4;&#x03BF;&#x0301;&#x03C2;</b> <b>stratos</b> (an <i>army</i>; from the base of <a href=\"#/G4766 - στρώννυμι - strṓnnymi - strone'-noo-mee/4766\">G4766</a>, as <i>encamped</i>); <i>camp likeness</i>, that is, an <i>army</i>, that is, (figuratively) the <i>angels</i>, the celestial <i>luminaries:</i> - host.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G4752/4752\">G4752</a>, <a href=\"#/G4753/4753\">G4753</a>, <a href=\"#/G4754/4754\">G4754</a>, <a href=\"#/G4755/4755\">G4755</a>, <a href=\"#/G4756/4756\">G4756</a>, <a href=\"#/G4757/4757\">G4757</a>, <a href=\"#/G4758/4758\">G4758</a>, <a href=\"#/G4759/4759\">G4759</a>, <a href=\"#/G4760/4760\">G4760</a>"}]}